NAME
    Acme::CPANModules::ManagingMultipleRepositories - List of tools to
    manage multiple repositories

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.002 of
    Acme::CPANModules::ManagingMultipleRepositories (from Perl distribution
    Acme-CPANModules-ManagingMultipleRepositories), released on 2023-10-29.

DESCRIPTION
    This Acme::CPANModules list catalogs tools to manage multiple
    repositories.

    Keywords: git, vcs, cvs

    1. On CPAN

    1.a git only

    gitbunch from Git::Bunch

    got from App::GitGot

    group-git from Group::Git

    *1.b VCS-agnostic*

    TBD

    2. Outside CPAN

    2.a git only

    TBD

    2.b VCS-agnostic

    mr, <http://joeyh.name/code/mr>

ACME::CPANMODULES ENTRIES
    Git::Bunch
        Author: PERLANCAR <https://metacpan.org/author/PERLANCAR>

